-- BP Drops as Cost of Response to Gulf of Mexico Spill Climbs to $2 Billion
-- Stephen Cunningham
-- 2010-06-21T07:07:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-21/bp-declines-as-much-as-2-6-in-london-trading-as-cost-of-gulf-spill-mounts.html

          
          
             BP Plc fell as much as 2.6 percent
in London trading as the company said the cost of the response
to the spill has reached about $2 billion.  
          
          


  


        